<h2>Notification Settings Update</h2>
<p>Dear {{userName}},</p>

<div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px;">
    <p>Your notification settings have been updated:</p>
    <ul>
        {{#each settings}}
        <li>{{type}}: {{#if enabled}}Enabled{{else}}Disabled{{/if}}</li>
        {{/each}}
    </ul>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 20px;">You can update these settings anytime from your profile settings page.</p>